# LoLDatabaseAPI

LoLDatabaseAPI is a simple and friendly to use API allowing the League of Legends developer community to access to all League of Legend game data in the most convenient way possible.

## Get All Champions [/champions]

### /champions [GET]

Fetches info for all champions

+ Response 200 (application/json)

        "example": [
            {
                "id": "Aatrox",
                "lore": "Tell me again, ...",
                "championsStats": [
                    "health": 1234,
                    "attackDamage": 341,
                    ...
                ]
                "recommended" : 
                    "items": [
                        {
                            "count": 1,
                            "id": "Duskbalde"
                        },
                        {
                            "count": 1,
                            "id": "BoTRK"
                        },
                        {
                            "count": 3,
                            "id": "Potions"
                        }
                    ],
                "Lore": "..."
                "GameModes": {
                    "Normals": true,
                    "Ranked": true,
                    "ARAM": true,
                }
            },
            {
                "id": "4293472123",
                "recommended" : 
                    "items": [
                        {
                            "count": 1,
