## Get Specific Champion [/champions/{champion}]

### /champions/{champion} [GET]

Fetches info for a specific champion

+ Parameters
    + champion (string, required)  - champion name in all lower case no spaces


+ Response 200 (application/json)

        "example": [
            {
                "id": "Aatrox",
                "recommended" : 
                    "items": [
                        {
                            "count": 1,
                            "name": "BoTRK"
                        },
                        {
                            "count": 1,
                            "id": "Duskblade"
                        },
                        {
                            "count": 3,
                            "id": "Potions"
                        }
                    ],
                "Lore" : "..."
                "GameModes": {
                    "Normals": true,
                    "Ranked": true,
                    "ARAM": true,
                    "StarGaurdian": false
                }
            }
        ]

+ Response 404 (application/json)

        { 
            "error": "Resource not found" 
        }
        
