## Get Game Mode [/gameModes/{gameMode}]
    
### /gameModes/{gameMode} [GET]

Fetches info for a game mode

+ Parameter
    + gameMode (number, required) - String game mode all lower case, using dashes instead of space
        1. Summoner's Rift
        2. Howling Abyss
        3. Twisted Treeline
    
+ Response 200 (applicaton/json)
    
        "example": [
            "Summoners Rift": {
                "MapImg": "http://url.png"
                "Lore": "will populate with real lore",
                "InGameDescription": "The newest and most...",
                "Versions": [
                    "Summer Version": "It's the first...",
                    "Winter Version": "A variant of the..."
                ],
                "Development": "Summoner Rift evolves...",
                "Playable Champions": [
                    "Lux",
                    "Aatrox",
                    "Caitlyn",
                    "etc."
                ],
                "Items": [
                    "Duskblade",
                    "BoTRK",
                    "etc."
                ]
            }
        ]
        
+ Response 404 (application/json)

        { 
            "error": "Resource not found" 
        }
        
