## Match Details [/matches/matchHistory/{matchID}]

### /matches/matchHistory/{matchID} [GET]

Fetches details about a specific match.

+ Parameter
    + matchID (number) - ID of the match you are looking up

+ Response 200 (application/json)
    
        "example": [
            "matchDetails": {
                "MatchID: 4819434182,
                "Participants": {
